gal opinions of the secretariats of the United Nations and related intergovernmental organizations", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Part Three. Judicial decisions on questions relating to the United Nations and related intergovernmental organizations", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Chapter VII. Decisions of international tribunals", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Chapter VIII. Decisions of national tribunals", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Part Four. Legal bibliography of the United Nations and related intergovernmental organizations", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "3007 (XXVII). Composition of the Secretariat", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "The General Assembly,", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Having considered the composition of the Secretariat36 and the long-term recruitment plan,37", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Desirous of ensuring that, in accordance with Article 8 of the Charter of the United Nations, no restrictions are placed on the eligibility of men and women to participate in any capacity and under conditions of equality in the work of the Secretariat,", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Desirous further of avoiding any discrimination between staff members on grounds of sex,", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "Requests the Secretary-General to submit to the General Assembly at its twenty-eighth session a study on those provisions of the Staff Rules and Staff Regulations of the United Nations whose application might, in certain cases, give rise to discrimination between staff members on grounds of sex.", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": null, "action_verb_type": null, "action_verb_normalized": null, "links": []}, {"text": "2113th plenary meeting", "type": "backmatter", "language": "english", "heading_level": null, "paragraph_type": null, "paragraph_level": null, "prefix": null, "action_verb": 